      throws IOException
        Read JSON data associated with this property and apply it to the provided objectInstance on which this property exists.

        The parser's current token is expected to be the JsonToken.FIELD_NAME for the field value being parsed.

        After parsing the parser's current token will be the next token after the field's value.

        Parameters:
        objectInstance - an instance of the class on which this property exists
        context - the JSON parsing context
        Returns:
        true if the property was parsed, or false if the data did not contain information for this property
        Throws:
        IOException - if there was an error when reading JSON data
